Description.value: This integration flow receives information about changes to insurance policies and contracts including the effective dates of the changes. It checks whether the information is of relevance to SAP Commerce, financial services accelerator, reads detailed information about the changed versions from Policy Management in SAP S/4HANA, and provides this data to SAP Commerce, financial services accelerator.

name.value: Replicate Insurance Policy Information from Policy Management in SAP S4HANA to SAP Hybris Commerce FSA
